title: HOUR 2 - Dwight Freeney, Eric Mangini
itunes:title: HOUR 2 - Dwight Freeney, Eric Mangini
description:
In hour 2, Dwight Freeney joins to talk Rookie QBs and the expectations set for them. Eric Mangini joins to talk more about the Bucs vs Patriots and the relationship between Robert Kraft and Bill Belichick.
